company_name: MEERKRONE FISCH - FEINKOST GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG
information: The company MEERKRONE FISCH - FEINKOST GESELLSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER HAFTUNG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1968, which operates in the Fish, tinned industry. It also operates in the Fish, processing industries. It is based in Lübeck, Germany.
